==English==

===Noun===
#(obsolete) Prior to [[police force]]s, a person appointed by a town or city to walk the streets at night and guard the [[burgher]]s from felons and robbers.
#A person who [[guard]]s (usually at a building) at night.
#{{Cricket}} The last [[batsman]] in a three or five day game to play on a particular day and thus carry over the [[batting]] to the following day.

